{"tid":2279677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10 名休班警員違反限聚令 警長承認普通襲擊罪被判 160 小時社會服務令","createTime":"2020-11-10T03:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T03:11:19.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"985b4b8758771207fa1dbd33b5f8858486383d93","tid":2279677,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"10 名休班警員違反限聚令，於今年 4 月 19 日凌晨，在元朗食肆「食宵夜」為一名女警送行。女警向警長梁珏榮敬酒，惟梁拒絕及遭女警揶揄，兩人爭執期間，女警用紅酒濺濕警長鞋子，梁遂扯她頭髮 10 秒。該名警長早前承認普通襲擊罪，今（10 日）在屯門裁判法院被判 160 小時社會服務令。裁判官水佳麗指社會服務令報告良好，當中列舉被告因家庭因素、壓力下犯案，但歸根究底，犯案原因只有兩個字「驕傲」，又指事主的頭皮有腫，證明被告動作是不留情、不留手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%B5%E5%A4%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E7%B4%85%E9%85%92%E6%BF%BA%E9%9E%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E6%89%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%8D%E9%A0%AD%E9%AB%AE%E5%88%A4-160-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%A4-%E5%AE%98-%E7%8A%AF%E6%A1%88%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%97-%E9%A9%95%E5%82%B2/?fbclid=IwAR3O2Ispyy1fpahsD2-oTDe6Xy6_TSHiUu5m1q-RqPmbXC7usFCOCuOndwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%25B5%25E5%25A4%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%2585%2592%25E6%25BF%25BA%25E9%259E%258B-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%2589%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25A2%258D%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E9%25AB%25AE%25E5%2588%25A4-160-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%258D%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%2597-%25E9%25A9%2595%25E5%2582%25B2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3O2Ispyy1fpahsD2-oTDe6Xy6_TSHiUu5m1q-RqPmbXC7usFCOCuOndwU&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y2yAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=c3548a5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%25B5%25E5%25A4%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%2585%2592%25